These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
House: craftsman, townhouse, futuristic, colonial
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, blueberry, plum, pomegranate
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, musician, firefighter, lawyer
City: london, berlin, rome, colone
1. the musician is the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the firefighter is between the futuristic house and the colonial house##2
3. the musician is the person traveling to london##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the bartender##1
6. the person traveling to rome is the futuristic house##1
7. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the colonial house##1
8. the bartender is on the far right##1
9. the townhouse house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| House   | townhouse | colonial   | craftsman  | futuristic  |
| Food   | blueberry    | pomegranate    | asparagus      | plum    |
| Job   | lawyer | musician | firefighter | bartender |
| City     | colone  | london       | berlin    | rome     |

