.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different games are played: domino, backgammon, whist, billiard
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, roller, bus, ship
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, game, prince, swisher
House: wooden, colonial, cape-cod, victorian
1. the victorian house is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
3. the swisher-smoker is the colonial house##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person driving the ship is between the prince-smoker and the wooden house##2
6. the victorian house is between the person driving the ship and the swisher-smoker##2
7. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person playing whist##1
9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Game         | billiard | backgammon    | whist  | domino    |
| Transport   | bike      | roller  | ship  | bus |
| Cigar           | swisher      | prince       | game      | dannemann       |
| House         | colonial    | victorian | cape-cod | wooden |

