.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, sports, action, documentary
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, tiparillo, havana, pall-mall
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, september, february, july
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, egyptian, japanese, colombian
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the egyptian##1
2. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the japanese is on the left of the egyptian##1
4. the egyptian is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is the pall-mall-smoker##1
7. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is between the game-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##2
9. the havana-smoker is between the person watching action movies and the person who's birthday is in september##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre        | sports | action     | time-travel   | documentary     |
| Cigar       | tiparillo   | game   | havana | pall-mall |
| Birthday         | june   | february | july       | september    |
| Nationality   | japanese    | egyptian | pakistani  | colombian    |

