.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, purple, light-blue, mauve
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, billiard, poker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, iced-tea, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, gardening, cooking, drawing
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing poker is the person who likes white##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing poker is the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes light-blue##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person who likes purple is between the person drinking juice and the person who likes mauve##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Color           | white  | mauve | purple     | light-blue |
| Game   | poker | mah-jongg  | billiard | backgammon       |
| Beverage           | mirinda       | water    | iced-tea      | juice           |
| Hobby         | singing | gardening   | drawing   | cooking         |

