.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different games are played: canasta, billiard, domino, go
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, jet-ski, train, helicopter
City: prague, paris, venice, new-york
4 different pets are kept: pony, rabbit, turtle, frog
 1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the train is the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person playing go##1
 6. the person playing domino is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person playing domino is between the owner of the frog and the person traveling to prague##2
10. the person traveling to venice is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Game          | billiard         | domino         | canasta     | go      |
| Transport           | train | helicopter | taxi    | jet-ski     |
| City   | prague      | venice       | new-york    | paris       |
| Pet         | pony     | turtle       | frog | rabbit |

