2. the person driving the scooter is between the owner of the mouse and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the siglo-smoker and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Transport           | taxi | scooter | subway  | bike |
