 4. the owner of the snake is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 7. the cain-smoker is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the fonseca-smoker is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game   | backgammon | billiard | whist  | poker  |
| Pet   | goat       | snake   | lizard | rabbit    |
| Cigar   | cain   | fonseca   | aristoff | game |
